# PORTFOLIO SPRINT 01 - Balanced Roadmap & Sprint Allocation Report - 2026-06-04

## Executive Summary

PORTFOLIO SPRINT 01 converts the RECAST 01 maturity audit into an ordered execution queue. The allocation prioritizes structural recovery first, controlled L3/L4 advancement second, and HOLD/backlog control for mature or execution-sensitive nuclei.

No runtime implementation was performed. No nucleus is production-ready or execution-authorized.

