## Per-Nucleus Next Work

- ACS: HOLD backlog control, dependency/risk documentation only.
- Academy: L5 contract/read-model consolidation without credential/reward execution.
- AxodusAPP: L5 real-data readiness plan without real execution.
- BBA-Agency: L3 mock/local validation and claim-review recovery.
- Business: L5 contract/read-only approval model consolidation.
- Core: L6 backlog criteria and consumer certification map only.
- Defi: L5 non-executing Phase 3 contract/interface planning.
- Dex: L4 read-only/no-swap visibility planning.
- Documentation: structural nucleus recovery.
- Governance: HOLD backlog control, no API transport implementation.
- Lottery: controlled L3 recovery with compliance/randomness/payout gates.
- Marketplace: L6 readiness gap analysis with no payments/settlement.
- Mining: L4 visibility and provider boundary consolidation.
- Trading: HOLD backlog control, credential-vault planning only.
- Global Docs / Instructions: versioning/ownership/source-of-truth recovery.

## Per-Nucleus Blocked Work

- ACS: runtime mutation, Hummingbot control, trading, treasury movement, credential access, Governance/Core bypass.
- Academy: real credential issuance, reward execution, minting, transfers, withdrawals.
- AxodusAPP: real execution, wallet signing, production backend switching, treasury, settlement.
- BBA-Agency: production campaigns, real billing, external automation execution, payment flows.
- Business: real approvals, persistence promotion, production business execution, financial commitments.
- Core: execution authority, treasury controls, product decisions, production runtime authority.
- Defi: custody, staking execution, rebalancing, validator scoring execution, fund movement.
- Dex: swaps, routing execution, settlement, linked fork mutation, token-list repo mutation.
- Documentation: official release publishing without approval and product behavior changes.
- Governance: API transport implementation, HTTP routes/controllers, real DB, AxodusAPP real client, executor, treasury, on-chain writes.
- Lottery: prize execution, payouts, treasury movement, production VRF, contract deployment, on-chain writes.
- Marketplace: wallet transactions, blockchain writes, payment gateways, treasury, settlement, minting, value transfer.
- Mining: provider custody, accounting execution, treasury, payout execution, real provider execution.
- Trading: live trading, real keys, withdrawals, production KMS/HSM, production DB, treasury, vendor changes.
- Global Docs / Instructions: Git init, root move, destructive restructuring, deleting reports.

